## 3. Lookup Endpoints (Populate Dropdowns)

Call these when the dashboard loads to populate dropdowns. Both work with JWT or static bearer.

### List Courses
```
GET /api/v1/dallah/courses
```
Response `200`:
```json
{
  "courses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "course_name": "Private Driving - Arabic",
      "dallah_course_code": "P6h",
      "language": "Arabic",
      "category": "private"
    }
  ]
}
```
Use `dallah_course_code` + `language` + `category` when submitting enrollment requests.

### List Branches
```
GET /api/v1/dallah/branches
```
Response `200`:
```json
{
  "branches": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "branch_id": 6,
      "branch_name": "Riyadh",
      "section_id": 10,
      "section_name": "Central"
    }
  ]
}
```
Use `branch_id` as the `school_id` when creating users.

