## 6. Notifications (Attendance / Progress View)
```
GET /api/v1/dallah/notifications
```
Returns up to 100 unprocessed notifications (oldest first).

Response `200`:
```json
{
  "notifications": [
    {
      "id": 42,
      "event_type": "enrollment_outcome",
      "created_at": "2026-03-08T10:00:00Z",
      "enrollment": {
        "aanaab_user_id": 123,
        "enrollment_id": 5,
        "workflow_state": "active",
        "total_progress": 0.25
      }
    }
  ],
  "meta": { "count": 1, "has_more": false }
}
```

`created_at` on the notification = when the user started the course.  
Use `meta.has_more` to show a "load more" indicator.

